{"tid":1477272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想為勇武派建立軍規，可以啊","createTime":"2019-08-16T05:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:19:45.000Z","uid":57076,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8f59c1821bae900ca04614d0a6a2a82e9acacc11","tid":1477272,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"首先，承認香港係戰亂時刻，我地係緊打仗，唔係講咩軍規? 軍隊武器，軍糧呢?<br />\n<br />\n第二，想建立軍規班大台既人，你夠膽企第一排做肉盾，勇武派實會服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n犯軍規既手足會點? 係咪要會有懲罰? <br />\n係咪雨傘運動篤灰2.0進化版?<br />\n前線打生打死，仲要花精神處理大台空降而黎既軍規。<br />\n<br />\n出面都有人講，連藍絲同班狗都識槍頭對外啦，大台班人又想搞軍規仲講不分化不割蔗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要講教條? 我地淨係會信一句:<br />\nNothing is true,everything is permitted.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n一日未成功，我地都會進行繼續抗爭，唔會受所謂軍規制約。"},{"pid":"f70b747dfdfac686a6b85f7751e91248aba2799a","tid":1477272,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a660e0dba56c86fb5bb2561b2a809e5276ec9df7","tid":1477272,"uid":50719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"雨傘怨靈陰魂不散<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZrHTtz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZrHTtz.png&h=bda7438a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ef070a70a94cb758f0686224702a3f83ea5d35e","tid":1477272,"uid":67454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:44:50.000Z","msg":".....nothing is true everything is permitted <br />\n之外都有3條守則啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQG1pCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQG1pCO.jpg&h=5ed8d7fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1de990ba4373ddc140993385904a7ee9093f2226","tid":1477272,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit